y of them, and they were usually on 'bottom' side of branches. Does anyone know what this could be?<\/p>\n\n<p>I took a photo:<\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://i.stack.imgur.com/gQcZQ.jpg\" alt=\"Kongens Have photo\"><\/p>\n\n<p>I suspect some pupa of insects, but it is just a quess.  <\/p>\n","question_id":2970,"tags":["entomology","species-identification"],"score":10,"accepted_answer_id":2972,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":358,"up_vote_count":10,"last_edit_date":1343006461},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Bl4QI.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":1158,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/1158/adolfo-perez","reputation":144,"display_name":"Adolfo Perez"},"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/33af7b8879cdcdfdb5edb7b1f265fd9c?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":430,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/430/richard-smith-unna","reputation":7703,"display_name":"Richard Smith-Unna","accept_rate":90},"score":3,"post_id":2937,"edited":false,"creation_date":1342909185,"comment_id":4345,"body":"Your question is very vague. Energy efficient compared to what? What makes you think they are &#39;so&#39; energy efficient? You should try to explain why you&#39;re asking the question, as in its current state is has no context."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/8729233d525a654914051bf8c1234c78?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":115,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/115/nico","reputation":6011,"display_name":"nico","accept_rate":100},"score":0,"post_id":2937,"edited":false,"creation_date":1342949389,"comment_id":4355,"body":"-1: please improve your question by better specifying what you are comparing insects to (birds? planes? or...?)"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Bl4QI.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":1158,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/